  "text": "The 2 x 2 blocks have exclusively complex conjugate pairs of eigenvalues. The ordering of blocks is generally arbitrary and can be changed by using appropriate orthogonal reordering techniques [CITATION_1] . We assume that A is already in a RSF.",
